To hack sublime 3 (version 3.2.2 build 3211) follow bellow steps:

1. give the execution permission for the bas.sh script and then run it
	to prevent that the license get blocked

2. copy the license file into the folder under the path of
	".config/sublime-text-3/Local" inside of your user home dir

NOTE: To check what is your user home directory, type in the terminal following
			command: echo $HOME

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Optional steps (in case if the license file won't work), instead of step 2 do:

1. Open the included Sublime 3
2. From the Help menu select: "Enter license" (or similiar)
3. Type bellow text into the field:

----- BEGIN LICENSE -----
TwitterInc
200 User License
